{"tid":1418664,"cid":25,"subCid":0,"title":"貓貓痾唔到尿！！！","createTime":"2019-08-05T19:40:50.000Z","updateTime":"2019-08-07T12:04:14.000Z","uid":177641,"like":10,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":9,"replies":[{"pid":"f9c62cfad0ca9d04492123d7bc6790fd5bd79be5","tid":1418664,"uid":177641,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-05T19:40:50.000Z","msg":"男貓嚟嘅<br />\n早排成日喺被到痾尿 有成攤尿嘅<br />\n但喺自己個貓廁痾就得一兩滴<br />\n但佢成日又去得好密<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n水又唔肯飲 要用放幾粒糧喺水入面先吸引到佢<br />\n<br />\n會唔會係膀胱發炎定係腎病<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />？<br />\n上網睇有人話柏圖獸醫幾好 有冇巴打試過<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n聽日再痾唔到就去睇醫生<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b2c2475e308c50831d46096635c389a325649c6d","tid":1418664,"uid":213295,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-05T19:43:08.000Z","msg":"有機會生石"},{"pid":"2db3bf51983981efd935a33cec05ccba2ecce74f","tid":1418664,"uid":177641,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"b2c2475e308c50831d46096635c389a325649c6d","tid":1418664,"uid":213295,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-05T19:43:08.000Z","msg":"有機會生石"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-05T19:45:14.000Z","msg":"佢胃口仲好好<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />引到佢飲晒兜水都痾唔到"},{"pid":"8a09c72b0bc706ad64dc19d77ca9de0a076e3738","tid":1418664,"uid":261201,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-05T19:48:31.000Z","msg":"痾唔到尿好危險，會致命<br />\n盡快帶主子睇醫生"},{"pid":"13e0365ada85e6d9745ceeb256e5a771d564c721","tid":1418664,"uid":17530,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"f9c62cfad0ca9d04492123d7bc6790fd5bd79be5","tid":1418664,"uid":177641,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-05T19:40:50.000Z","msg":"男貓嚟嘅<br />\n早排成日喺被到痾尿 有成攤尿嘅<br />\n但喺自己個貓廁